    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="1-创建主、从安装目录"><a href="#1-创建主、从安装目录" class="headerlink" title="1. 创建主、从安装目录"></a>1. 创建主、从安装目录</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> -p /data/mysql/mysql-master/&#123;data,bin-log,slow_log,error_log&#125;<br><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> -p /data/mysql/mysql-slave/&#123;data,bin-log,slow_log,error_log&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="2-系统mariadb-处理"><a href="#2-系统mariadb-处理" class="headerlink" title="2. 系统mariadb 处理"></a>2. 系统mariadb 处理</h3><p>[检查 Linux 系统有 mariadb，则需要根据其&#x2F;etc&#x2F;my. cnf 创建并授权 mariadb. log]</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash">vim /etc/my.cnf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![[Pasted image 20250227102818.png]]<br>创建对应目录和文件并授权 <span style="background:#ff4d4f">&#x2F;var&#x2F;log&#x2F;mariadb&#x2F;mariadb. log</span></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建目录</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">mkdir</span> -p /var/log/mariadb<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建文件</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">touch</span> /var/log/mariadb/mariadb.log<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 授权</span><br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 /var/log/mariadb/mariadb.log<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="3-解压-MySql-安装包到主目录和从目录"><a href="#3-解压-MySql-安装包到主目录和从目录" class="headerlink" title="3. 解压 MySql 安装包到主目录和从目录"></a>3. 解压 MySql 安装包到主目录和从目录</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">cd</span> /data/mysql/<br><br>tar -xvf mysql-8.0.37-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.xz<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> -a /data/mysql/mysql-8.0.37-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64/* /data/mysql/mysql-master/<br><span class="hljs-built_in">cp</span> -a /data/mysql/mysql-8.0.37-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64/* /data/mysql/mysql-slave/<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">rm</span> -rf /data/mysql/mysql-8.0.37-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="4-编辑-MySql-mysql-server-服务脚本"><a href="#4-编辑-MySql-mysql-server-服务脚本" class="headerlink" title="4. 编辑 MySql[mysql. server]服务脚本"></a>4. 编辑 MySql[mysql. server]服务脚本</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 主 /data/mysql/mysql-master/support-files/mysql.server</span><br>vim /data/mysql/mysql-master/support-files/mysql.server<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 从 /data/mysql/mysql-slave/support-files/mysql.server</span><br>vim /data/mysql/mysql-slave/support-files/mysql.server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改 46、47 行<br>主：</p><figure class="highlight haskell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haskell"><span class="hljs-title">basedir</span>=/<span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">data</span>/mysql/mysql-master/</span><br><span class="hljs-title">datadir</span>=/<span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">data</span>/mysql/mysql-master/<span class="hljs-keyword">data</span>/</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>从：</p><figure class="highlight haskell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs haskell"><span class="hljs-title">basedir</span>=/<span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">data</span>/mysql/mysql-slave/</span><br><span class="hljs-title">datadir</span>=/<span class="hljs-class"><span class="hljs-keyword">data</span>/mysql/mysql-slave/<span class="hljs-keyword">data</span>/</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>![[Pasted image 20250227105916.png]]<br>修改后执行</p><figure class="highlight swift"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs swift">sed <span class="hljs-operator">-</span>i &#x27;s<span class="hljs-regexp">/\r$/</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/&#x27; /</span>data<span class="hljs-regexp">/mysql/</span>mysql<span class="hljs-operator">-</span>master<span class="hljs-regexp">/support-files/</span>mysql.server<br><br>sed <span class="hljs-operator">-</span>i &#x27;s<span class="hljs-regexp">/\r$/</span><span class="hljs-regexp">/&#x27; /</span>data<span class="hljs-regexp">/mysql/</span>mysql<span class="hljs-operator">-</span>slave<span class="hljs-regexp">/support-files/</span>mysql.server<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="5-配置-my-cnf"><a href="#5-配置-my-cnf" class="headerlink" title="5. 配置 my. cnf"></a>5. 配置 my. cnf</h3><p>   路径：&#x2F;data&#x2F;mysql&#x2F;mysql-master&#x2F;my.cnf  |  &#x2F;data&#x2F;mysql&#x2F;mysql-slave&#x2F;my. cnf </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-comment"># 格式修正(去掉\r)</span><br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s/\r$//&#x27;</span> /data/mysql/mysql-master/my.cnf<br><br>sed -i <span class="hljs-string">&#x27;s/\r$//&#x27;</span> /data/mysql/mysql-slave/my.cnf<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>主数据配置：</p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs cnf">[主DB配置]<br>文件：/data/mysql/mysql-master/my.cnf<br>[mysqld]<br># 服务器标识ID<br>server_id=20001<br># 二进制日志文件<br>log_bin=/data/mysql/mysql-master/bin-log/bin-log<br># 设置logbin格式<br>binlog-format=ROW<br># 同步的数据库<br>binlog-do-db=&quot;iot&quot;<br># 设置3306端口<br>port=3306<br># 设置mysql的安装目录<br>basedir=/data/mysql/mysql-master<br># 设置mysql数据库的数据的存放目录<br>datadir=/data/mysql/mysql-master/data<br># PID文件<br>pid-file=/data/mysql/mysql-master/data/mysqld-master.pid<br># 客户端最大连接数<br>max_connections=1000<br># 允许连接失败的次数。这是为了防止有人从该主机试图攻击数据库系统<br>max_connect_errors=10<br># 服务端使用的字符集默认为UTF8<br>character-set-server=utf8mb4<br># 创建新表时将使用的默认存储引擎<br>default-storage-engine=INNODB<br># 默认使用“mysql_native_password”插件认证<br>default_authentication_plugin=mysql_native_password<br>lower_case_table_names=1<br>#错误日志文件,初始化时,生成的root用户密码<br>log-error=/data/mysql/mysql-master/error_log/mysql_error.log<br>#开启慢查询功能<br>slow_query_log=1 <br>#慢查询SQL日志<br>slow_query_log_file=/data/mysql/mysql-master/slow_log/mysql_slow_query.log<br>#慢查询超时时间,如果超过5秒认为是慢查询,并被记录到slow_query_log_file中<br>long_query_time=5<br>skip-external-locking<br>skip-name-resolve<br>socket=/tmp/mysqlmaster.sock<br>#默认存储引擎<br>default_storage_engine=InnoDB <br>innodb_autoinc_lock_mode=2<br>#开启事件功能定时任务等<br>event_scheduler=ON<br>default-time_zone=&#x27;+8:00&#x27;<br>#innodb存储引擎默认缓冲池大小(推荐服务器内存的一半)<br>innodb_buffer_pool_size=2G <br>innodb_buffer_pool_instances=4<br>read_buffer_size=32M<br>read_rnd_buffer_size=32M<br>join_buffer_size=32M<br>sort_buffer_size=64M<br>#读的IO线程数<br>innodb_read_io_threads=16 <br>#写的IO线程数<br>innodb_write_io_threads=16 <br>table_open_cache=4000<br>[mysql]<br># 设置mysql客户端默认字符集<br>default-character-set=utf8mb4<br>[client]<br># 设置mysql客户端连接服务端时默认使用的端口<br>port=3306<br>default-character-set=utf8mb4<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>从数据库配置：</p><figure class="highlight routeros"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br><span class="line">48</span><br><span class="line">49</span><br><span class="line">50</span><br><span class="line">51</span><br><span class="line">52</span><br><span class="line">53</span><br><span class="line">54</span><br><span class="line">55</span><br><span class="line">56</span><br><span class="line">57</span><br><span class="line">58</span><br><span class="line">59</span><br><span class="line">60</span><br><span class="line">61</span><br><span class="line">62</span><br><span class="line">63</span><br><span class="line">64</span><br><span class="line">65</span><br><span class="line">66</span><br><span class="line">67</span><br><span class="line">68</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs routeros">[从DB配置]<br>文件：/data/mysql/mysql-slave/my.cnf<br>[mysqld]<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 服务器标识ID</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">server_id</span>=20002<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 二进制日志文件</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">log_bin</span>=/data/mysql/mysql-slave/bin-log/bin-log<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 设置logbin格式</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">binlog-format</span>=ROW<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 启用中继日志</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">relay-log</span>=mysql-relay<br><span class="hljs-attribute">read-only</span>=<span class="hljs-literal">true</span><br><span class="hljs-comment"># 设置3307端口</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">port</span>=3307<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 设置mysql的安装目录</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">basedir</span>=/data/mysql/mysql-slave<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 设置mysql数据库的数据的存放目录</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">datadir</span>=/data/mysql/mysql-slave/data<br><span class="hljs-comment"># PID文件</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">pid-file</span>=/data/mysql/mysql-slave/data/mysqld-slave.pid<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 客户端最大连接数</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">max_connections</span>=1000<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 允许连接失败的次数。这是为了防止有人从该主机试图攻击数据库系统</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">max_connect_errors</span>=10<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 服务端使用的字符集默认为UTF8</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">character-set-server</span>=utf8mb4<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 创建新表时将使用的默认存储引擎</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">default-storage-engine</span>=INNODB<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 默认使用“mysql_native_password”插件认证</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">default_authentication_plugin</span>=mysql_native_password<br><span class="hljs-attribute">lower_case_table_names</span>=1<br><span class="hljs-comment">#错误日志文件,初始化时,生成的root用户密码</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">log-error</span>=/data/mysql/mysql-slave/error_log/mysql_error.log<br><span class="hljs-comment">#开启慢查询功能</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">slow_query_log</span>=1 <br><span class="hljs-comment">#慢查询SQL日志</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">slow_query_log_file</span>=/data/mysql/mysql-slave/slow_log/mysql_slow_query.log<br><span class="hljs-comment">#慢查询超时时间,如果超过5秒认为是慢查询,并被记录到slow_query_log_file中</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">long_query_time</span>=5<br>skip-external-locking<br>skip-name-resolve<br><span class="hljs-attribute">socket</span>=/tmp/mysqlslave.sock<br><span class="hljs-comment">#默认存储引擎</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">default_storage_engine</span>=InnoDB <br><span class="hljs-attribute">innodb_autoinc_lock_mode</span>=2<br><span class="hljs-comment">#开启事件功能定时任务等</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">event_scheduler</span>=ON<br><span class="hljs-attribute">default-time_zone</span>=<span class="hljs-string">&#x27;+8:00&#x27;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">#innodb存储引擎默认缓冲池大小(推荐服务器内存的一半)</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">innodb_buffer_pool_size</span>=2G <br><span class="hljs-attribute">innodb_buffer_pool_instances</span>=4<br><span class="hljs-attribute">read_buffer_size</span>=32M<br><span class="hljs-attribute">read_rnd_buffer_size</span>=32M<br><span class="hljs-attribute">join_buffer_size</span>=32M<br><span class="hljs-attribute">sort_buffer_size</span>=64M<br><span class="hljs-comment">#读的IO线程数</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">innodb_read_io_threads</span>=16 <br><span class="hljs-comment">#写的IO线程数</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">innodb_write_io_threads</span>=16 <br><span class="hljs-attribute">table_open_cache</span>=4000<br>[mysql]<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 设置mysql客户端默认字符集</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">default-character-set</span>=utf8mb4<br>[client]<br><span class="hljs-comment"># 设置mysql客户端连接服务端时默认使用的端口</span><br><span class="hljs-attribute">port</span>=3307<br><span class="hljs-attribute">default-character-set</span>=utf8mb4<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="6-更改文件夹权限"><a href="#6-更改文件夹权限" class="headerlink" title="6. 更改文件夹权限"></a>6. 更改文件夹权限</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs bash"><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 /data/mysql/mysql-master<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 /data/mysql/mysql-master/data<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 644 /data/mysql/mysql-master/my.cnf<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 /data/mysql/mysql-master/error_log<br><br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 /data/mysql/mysql-slave<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 /data/mysql/mysql-slave/data<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 644 /data/mysql/mysql-slave/my.cnf<br><span class="hljs-built_in">chmod</span> -R 777 /data/mysql/mysql-slave/error_log<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="7-创建用户及用户组"><a href="#7-创建用户及用户组" class="headerlink" title="7. 创建用户及用户组"></a>7. 创建